      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那Event和Reminder需要持久化吗？我假设需要EventDAO来处理事件存储，ReminderService来处理提醒调度，这样结构更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
